reviewText: This is a Fantastic TV seires Great visaul animation ,a very touching and emotional show with great voice acyers added to the Characters,

That isn't to say that I dislike the content, the show is excellent. The packaging is top notch. I suppose it is my mistake for assuming that for $50 I would be getting more than the first episode. Interested buyers, you read that correctly: this is only the first episode of the show. I would still highly recommend giving this a watch, it is on Netflix currently.
